#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:8
msgid ""
"This page is the authoritative spec for the `perry.nativeLibrary` field a "
"native-bindings package declares in its `package.json`. The Perry compiler "
"reads this manifest at resolve time and uses it to:"
