msgstr ""

#: src/threading/spawn.md:184
msgid ""
"// ── Perry: 1 line ─────────────────────────────────────\n"
"// const result = await spawn(() => heavyComputation(inputData));\n"
msgstr ""

#: src/threading/spawn.md:189
msgid ""
"No separate files. No message ports. No event handlers. No structured clone."
" One line."
msgstr ""
"Không có file riêng biệt. Không có message port. Không có event handler. "
