#: src/platforms/linux.md:7
msgid ""
"GTK4 + libshumate (MapView) + GStreamer (audio playback) development "
"libraries. The release-packages CI pins to these and a build-from-source "
"fails without them. Cairo comes in as a transitive dep of GTK4 on every "
"distro."
