#: src/container/compose.md:1
msgid "Compose Orchestration (`perry/compose`)"
msgstr "Điều phối Compose (`perry/compose`)"

#: src/container/compose.md:3
msgid ""
"`perry/compose` brings the `docker compose up / down / ps / exec / logs` "
"workflow into TypeScript. The spec is a TS object literal that mirrors the "
"[Compose Specification](https://github.com/compose-spec/compose-"
"spec/blob/main/schema/compose-spec.json), the engine is in-process Rust (no "
"shell-out to a `docker-compose` binary), and dependency ordering / rollback "
"/ interpolation all run natively."
msgstr ""
"`perry/compose` đưa quy trình làm việc `docker compose up / down / ps / exec"
" / logs` vào TypeScript. Spec là một object literal TS phản ánh [Compose "
"Specification](https://github.com/compose-spec/compose-"
"spec/blob/main/schema/compose-spec.json), engine là Rust in-process (không "
"gọi shell ra binary `docker-compose`), và thứ tự phụ thuộc / rollback / nội "
"suy đều chạy natively."

#: src/container/compose.md:10
msgid "Bringing up a single-service stack"
msgstr "Khởi động stack với một dịch vụ"

#: src/container/compose.md:41
msgid ""
"The handle returned from `up()` is an opaque integer (NaN-boxed with "
"`POINTER_TAG`); pass it as the first argument to [`down`](#tearing-down) / "
"[`ps`](#status--logs--exec) / [`logs`](#status--logs--exec) / "
"[`exec`](#status--logs--exec). The template-string interpolation `${stack}` "
"renders as `[object Object]` because of the NaN-boxing tag; coerce "
"explicitly with `String(stack)` if you need to log it."
msgstr ""
"Handle trả về từ `up()` là một số nguyên mờ đục (NaN-boxed với "
"`POINTER_TAG`); truyền nó làm đối số đầu tiên cho [`down`](#tearing-down) / "
"[`ps`](#status--logs--exec) / [`logs`](#status--logs--exec) / "
"[`exec`](#status--logs--exec). Nội suy template-string `${stack}` hiển thị "
"là `[object Object]` do tag NaN-boxing; hãy ép kiểu tường minh bằng "
"`String(stack)` nếu bạn cần ghi log."

#: src/container/compose.md:49
msgid "Multi-service stack with healthcheck-gated startup"
msgstr "Stack đa dịch vụ với khởi động được kiểm soát bởi healthcheck"

#: src/container/compose.md:51
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { up as upMulti } from \"perry/compose\";\n"
"\n"
"async function bringUpMultiServiceStack(): Promise<void> {\n"
"    // depends_on with `condition: 'service_healthy'` blocks the\n"
"    // dependent service until the dependency's healthcheck reports\n"
"    // healthy. Use the map form (not the bare-array form) to pass\n"
"    // the condition.\n"
"    await upMulti({\n"
"        version: \"3.8\",\n"
"        services: {\n"
"            db: {\n"
"                image: \"postgres:16-alpine\",\n"
"                container_name: \"app-db\", // stable DNS target for siblings\n"
"                environment: {\n"
"                    POSTGRES_USER:     \"app\",\n"
"                    POSTGRES_PASSWORD: \"${APP_DB_PASSWORD:-changeme}\",\n"
"                    POSTGRES_DB:       \"app\",\n"
"                },\n"
"                volumes: [\"app-pgdata:/var/lib/postgresql/data\"],\n"
"                networks: [\"app-db-net\"],\n"
"                healthcheck: {\n"
"                    test: [\"CMD-SHELL\", \"pg_isready -U app -d app\"],\n"
"                    interval: \"5s\",\n"
"                    timeout: \"3s\",\n"
"                    retries: 10,\n"
"                    start_period: \"30s\",\n"
"                },\n"
"            },\n"
"            api: {\n"
"                image: \"myorg/api:1.0\",\n"
"                depends_on: { db: { condition: \"service_healthy\" } },\n"
"                environment: {\n"
"                    DATABASE_URL: \"postgres://app:changeme@app-db:5432/app\",\n"
"                },\n"
"                ports: [\"8080:8080\"],\n"
"                networks: [\"app-db-net\", \"app-web-net\"],\n"
"                restart: \"unless-stopped\",\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"        networks: {\n"
"            \"app-db-net\":  { driver: \"bridge\", internal: true }, // db unreachable from host\n"
"            \"app-web-net\": { driver: \"bridge\" },\n"
"        },\n"
"        volumes: {\n"
"            \"app-pgdata\": { driver: \"local\" },\n"
"        },\n"
"    });\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/compose.md:102
msgid "This pattern combines several production-grade primitives:"
msgstr "Pattern này kết hợp một số nguyên mẫu cấp độ production:"

#: src/container/compose.md:104
msgid "Primitive"
msgstr "Nguyên mẫu"

#: src/container/compose.md:106
msgid "`container_name: 'app-db'`"
msgstr "`container_name: 'app-db'`"

#: src/container/compose.md:106
msgid ""
"Forces a stable container name so docker's embedded DNS resolves `app-db` to"
" the postgres container's IP. **See the [DNS gotcha below](#cross-service-"
"dns-gotcha).**"
msgstr ""
"Buộc tên container cố định để DNS nhúng của docker phân giải `app-db` thành "
"địa chỉ IP của container postgres. **Xem [lưu ý về DNS bên dưới](#cross-"
"service-dns-gotcha).**"

#: src/container/compose.md:107
msgid "`healthcheck: { test: [...], interval, retries, start_period }`"
msgstr "`healthcheck: { test: [...], interval, retries, start_period }`"

#: src/container/compose.md:107
msgid ""
"Per-service liveness probe. Compose-spec § service.healthcheck shape — "
"Perry's engine honors it for `depends_on` gating."
msgstr ""
"Probe kiểm tra liveness theo từng service. Hình thức `service.healthcheck` "
"theo Compose-spec § — engine của Perry hỗ trợ nó để kiểm soát `depends_on`."

#: src/container/compose.md:108
msgid "`depends_on: { db: { condition: 'service_healthy' } }`"
msgstr "`depends_on: { db: { condition: 'service_healthy' } }`"

#: src/container/compose.md:108
msgid ""
"Holds the dependent service back until the dependency reports healthy. Three"
" valid conditions: `service_started`, `service_healthy`, "
"`service_completed_successfully`."
msgstr ""
"Giữ service phụ thuộc lại cho đến khi dependency báo cáo trạng thái healthy."
" Ba điều kiện hợp lệ: `service_started`, `service_healthy`, "
"`service_completed_successfully`."

#: src/container/compose.md:109
msgid "`networks: { ..., internal: true }`"
msgstr "`networks: { ..., internal: true }`"

#: src/container/compose.md:109
msgid ""
"Marks the network as internal-only — postgres is unreachable from the host "
"or from sibling stacks. See [Networking](./networking.md)."
msgstr ""
"Đánh dấu network là chỉ dùng nội bộ — postgres không thể truy cập từ host "
"hoặc từ các stack anh em. Xem [Networking](./networking.md)."

#: src/container/compose.md:110
msgid "`restart: 'unless-stopped'`"
msgstr "`restart: 'unless-stopped'`"

#: src/container/compose.md:110
msgid ""
"The runtime restarts the container after a crash, but not after an explicit "
"`docker stop`."
msgstr ""
"Runtime khởi động lại container sau khi crash, nhưng không khởi động lại sau"
" khi thực hiện `docker stop` tường minh."

#: src/container/compose.md:112
msgid ""
"The full `ComposeSpec` shape is exported from `perry/compose` as "
"`ComposeSpec`, with sub-types `Service`, `ComposeNetwork`, `ComposeVolume`, "
